originalText.text:
Ideally, I would give zero stars if google allowed that.

The level of care that patients receive here is really disappointing.  Not only do you have to sit here for hours on end, when you finally see this doctor, you're brushed off.  The ladies in the front aren't professional at all.  Seems like you're in a hair salon, rather than a doctors office.  Please do yourself a favor and find a different doctor for yourself or your loved one.  This place is an absolute joke.
